    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302340/extras/c8c9e3c16fd3a3d866b0030330a89123.poster.avif?t=1770687837\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302340/extras/c8c9e3c16fd3a3d866b0030330a89123.webm?t=1770687837\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302340/extras/c8c9e3c16fd3a3d866b0030330a89123.mp4?t=1770687837\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>动作与策略的完美结合</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在机甲争锋中，多达8名玩家可以在此展开激烈对战！玩家可随时在动作玩法和策略玩法之间切换。在你的指挥坦克中，你可以部署军队、释放强大技能；而当你想亲自参战时，可以随时化身英雄机甲加入战场！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302340/extras/0ea663f062a15ba68f68b344d88dfbc5.poster.avif?t=1770687837\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302340/extras/0ea663f062a15ba68f68b344d88dfbc5.webm?t=1770687837\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302340/extras/0ea663f062a15ba68f68b344d88dfbc5.mp4?t=1770687837\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>合作战役模式</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在1-4名玩家的合作Roguelite卡牌构筑模式中挑战BOSS、招募新队友、组建并升级你的战队以对抗蓝色军团的入侵！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302340/extras/85c7a7de73ea8d325fb7dbd357cef049.poster.avif?t=1770687837\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302340/extras/85c7a7de73ea8d325fb7dbd357cef049.webm?t=1770687837\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302340/extras/85c7a7de73ea8d325fb7dbd357cef049.mp4?t=1770687837\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>打造你的战队</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战斗开始前，你可以组建一副包含8张卡牌的战队。这些卡牌包括不同类型的部队、建筑，或者强大的技能卡。游戏中有超过30种卡牌可供选择，多种战术风格等你探索！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302340/extras/af3363e5b8764ea3f9b6f7381e6f32ff.poster.avif?t=1770687837\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302340/extras/af3363e5b8764ea3f9b6f7381e6f32ff.webm?t=1770687837\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302340/extras/af3363e5b8764ea3f9b6f7381e6f32ff.mp4?t=1770687837\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>专属机甲</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每位英雄都有独特的机甲！每台机甲配备有不同的武器与技能，选择与军队配合良好的机甲是取得胜利的关键！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>了解你的盟友</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一旦你将战队部署到战场上，他们将自动战斗，向敌方基地推进并攻击沿途的敌人。玩家可以与战队合作，收集有用的道具和武器，或者激活部队的特殊能力攻克敌军，赢得胜利！</p>",
